      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light swirling in the clear coat visible under direct sunlight. The interior is clean and smoke-free, showing only typical light wear on the driver's seat bolster and some minor scuffs on the door sills. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history. It is a reliable, attractive car that reflects its mileage and age honestly.",
