    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional find! This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving just as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail, from the flawless paint to the pristine interior, has been meticulously cared for, making it a perfect choice for a collector or anyone who demands the very best. It\u2019s a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection that\u2019s ready to be enjoyed immediately!",
