    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This absolute gem has been babied its whole life and is in truly pristine condition. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty\u2014it's seriously a rare find! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
