      "description": "Presenting a showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' aroma; the upholstery is pristine with no bolster wear or leather creasing, and all high-gloss trim pieces remain scratch-free. Every switch, sensor, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a complete portfolio of service records performed exclusively by certified specialists. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key collector-grade example that performs exactly as it did on the day of delivery.",
      "price": 44800.0,
